    "text": "This page covers comments, private Mia prompts, and background jobs. List comments Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with notes\\:read or admin . Returns saved comments for the note. Private Mia prompts are not returned. Create comment Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with comments\\:write or admin . Request: Response: a saved comment with 201 Created . Send a private Mia prompt Use the same endpoint, but start the body with @mia : Response: a prompt response with 200 OK . Mia prompt responses do not create jobs, do not save a shared comment, and do not update the note. Update comment Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with comments\\:write or admin . Admins can update any comment. Normal users can update only comments they created. Delete comment Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with comments\\:write or admin . Response: 204 No Content . Job object List jobs Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with notes\\:read or admin . Admins can see all jobs. Normal users see only their own jobs. Query parameters: | Parameter | Description | | | | | note id | Return jobs related to one note. | | status | Return jobs with a specific status. | Get job Authentication: session cookie or bearer token with notes\\:read or admin . Job statuses Agents should poll the job endpoint when file or URL parsing is pending."
